data.description: Welcome to 22420 Crest Forest Drive in Cedarpines Park area! Drive up to the drive-through parking area with a level entry into the home.  As you enter this open concept floor plan you'll find the kitchen, eating area and living room with a beautiful rock, wood burning fireplace for the cool weather in the winter time. In the kitchen there is laminate counter tops along with custom cabinets, 12 inch tile flooring, gas range, and more built-in cabinetry. In the living room, open the slider to go outside on the sealed deck to enjoy the mountain views and breathe in the mountain air. Also on this top level of the home is a bedroom and bathroom. Travel downstairs through the wide stairway into the family room, main bedroom with yet another fireplace with an insert, large laundry room, the third bedroom, second bathroom and bonus storage areas. You will also find dual pane windows throughout, some with security bars. Outside is a shed and more storage areas. This is a must see, come check it out!
